#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Kontact"
msgstr "Kontact"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:11
msgid ""
"Handle all your emails, calendars, contacts and more within a single window"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Handle your email, calendar, contacts and other personal data with Kontact. "
"Kontact groups everything together in one place and helps you manage your "
"communications, organize your day and work with your colleagues."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:16
msgid ""
"Kontact unifies several personal information management applications into a "
"single window to give you the best possible experience and boost your "
"productivity. With Kontact you can use all the tools of our powerful suite "
"in one place. Unlike proprietary web applications we value your privacy and "
"support open standards, which is why Kontact gives you full control over "
"your data. You can of course also access your data offline if you want to."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Kontact consists of several well-integrated components:"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:21
msgid ""
"KMail - a powerful and feature-rich email client with support for a wide "
"range of email providers."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"KOrganizer - a calendar and scheduling component of Kontact which is able to "
"work with NextCloud, Kolab, Google Calendar and other calendaring services."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:23
msgid ""
"KAddressBook - an easy to use contact management tool that can synchronize "
"contacts with many popular services."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:24
msgid ""
"Akregator - a news reader with powerful search and archiving functionality."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:38
msgid "KMail, the email component of Kontact"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:42
msgid ""
"Organize your time, manage events, create todos or schedule meetings with "
"KOrganizer"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:46
msgid "KAddressBook provides an easy way to manage your contacts"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kontact.appdata.xml:50
msgid "Stay on top of the new with Akregator, our news reader"
